Privacy Policy
Effective Date: 07/01/2024
Badlands Inc. ("we," "us," or "our") operates the Trashy Studio app. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and protect your information when you use our app.
1. Information We Collect
We do not collect any personal information from users when they use the Trashy Studio app. Users can use the app without creating an account or providing any personal information.
However, we do collect certain anonymous information through a bug reporter tool to help us improve the app and fix issues. This information includes:
Device type and model
Operating system version (e.g., iOS version)
App version
Anonymous usage data
2. Use of Your Information
The anonymous information collected through the bug reporter tool is used solely for the purpose of identifying and fixing bugs, improving app performance, and enhancing the user experience.
3. Sharing Your Information
We do not share any personal information because we do not collect any. The anonymous information collected through the bug reporter tool may be shared with our development team and third-party service providers who assist us in improving the app.
4. Data Security
We are committed to protecting your information. Although the information collected is anonymous, we still take measures to ensure it is protected against unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction.
5. Third-Party Services
The Trashy Studio app may contain links to third-party websites or services that we do not control. This Privacy Policy does not apply to third-party websites or services. We are not responsible for the privacy practices of any third party.
6. Children's Privacy
The Trashy Studio app is not intended for children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13. If we become aware that we have inadvertently received personal information from a user under the age of 13, we will delete such information from our records.
7. Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify users of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on our website at
trashystudio.co
. Your continued use of the Trashy Studio app after any changes indicates your acceptance of the new Privacy Policy.
8. Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at
hi@trashystudio.co
.